Realtime IRC Log with Gevent & Flask.

It is a toy project to learn web push technology.
Currently only support long-polling.
See : http://rtchatlog.labhijau.net

INSTALL
easy_install lib/oyoyo-0.8.tar.gz
easy_install http://code.google.com/p/gevent/downloads/detail?name=gevent-1.0b1.tar.gz&can=2&q=
pip install -r requirements.txt

RUNNING
cd thebot
rename botconf.py.template to botconf.py and fill nick & pasword
python oyobot.py

cd collector
python flask-collector.py 5252

cd rtlog
python logpoll.py

